效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"03803c61e087b12a0fc6f588ada5e7bfaebf7ba6","tid":1664754,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"ISIS搞搞佢"},{"pid":"7c3afd68ad6a23d8583912929c2138db9c76c802","tid":1664754,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"土耳其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77aba347b3470d7da5d6422f9d09b490d7548955","tid":1664754,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ah6h5GD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fah6h5GD.png&h=e5fcd496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//山哥透露，在 24 日事發當日，一行約 7 名「有槍有手扣」的便衣探員，到公園涼亭搜查是否有毒品或不法物品。山哥認得部分便衣警就是早前毆打過他的警員。這數名警員當時搭著山哥肩頭，把他拉到一旁說挑釁道：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">上次我哋打你，係咪好嬲呀？</span></span></strong>」。//<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\nDLLM 死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a3ef95af7ea324ec4cb4eeb1f29ff67fa0370a59","tid":1664754,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:11:53.000Z","ms